      "text": "Un wiꞥſch tohs ſwehti/\nka tee fohti watrojahs/ un wi-\nnu Lohpi ne nonihkfſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch tehs attak\nmaſus padarra/ ka tee apbehdi-\nnati tohp zaur Warras-Darbu/\nBlehdibu un Noskumschanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch mett Neewafcha-\nnn us Leeleen-Kungeein/ un leek\nteein allotees Tukschiba/kur Zet-\nta newaid.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet atweegina to Beh-\ndigu no wiꞥſa Behdahm/ un\neezelt wiꞥſa Raddu fa Awju\nPulku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee Sirde-Skatdee to\nredſche/ un preezafees/ un wiﬀai\nBlehdibai ta Mutte zeeſchi ja-\nturra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kurſch irr gudrs? lat tas\nto wehra Remin/ un lai tee ar\nSapraschanu nomanna ta\nKIUNGA Schehlastibas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": �,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta CVIII. Dseefma.\nIrr weena Pateikſchana Dahwida/ ka Deews\nwiannu attat fawa Walstiba eezehlis/ un\nprett wiſſeem Eenaidneeekeem lihdsſchim La-\nkam glahbis : 2 Tas gribbetu winnam\nwehl ioprohjam flahtſtaſweht un winna\nWalstibu apſtiprinaht 6. etc.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Eena Dahwida Dseet-\nima dfeedama.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ak Deews! ntan-\nna Sirde tre gattawa/ es\nfeedafchu un flawetchu ar Dseef-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": �,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "mahm/ manna Bohdiba a-\ndsan.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Mohdrinajeetes Sohi\nStabules un Rohkle/ es paſ-\nAufekti usino hdischobs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es pateikſchu tew/KUN-\nstarp teem Landim/es dseei-\ntchu tew starp tahm Tautah-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tawa Schehlastiba\nleela lihds patt Debbeſim/un\nwa Pateefiba lihds tahm au-\nſtahm Badebbetim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pa-augstinajees Dee-\npahr tahm Debbeſim/un ta-\nBohdiba pahr wiſſu Semini.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka tawi Mihkee tohp\nfwabbinati/atpeſti zaur ta-\nlabbu Rohku/un paklaufi ma-\nufs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Deews runna fawa five\nta Weeta/pahr to es preez-\njohs/es dallifchu Sikemu/u-\nmehroſchn to Eleiju Sukot-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Gtleads man peederr/\nManaſus man peederr/un E-\nwraims irr mannas Galwa-\nStiprums/Juhda irr man-\nWaldons.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Moabs irr mans ma-\ngajamajs Pohds/mannu Kur-\nſteeplu es pahr Eedomu/to Wi-\nlisteru Semme gawile ma-\npretti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas waddihs mann wee\nna ſtipra Pilſtahta? kas pawad-\ndihs mann lihds Eedomain?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Neggi tu Deews/ka-\ntu muhs eſſi atmettis/un ne iſ-\ngahjt ak Deews! ar muhſ-\n"
    }
  ],
